WEBVTT

00:01:27.536 --> 00:01:30.211
Rekoh, "Solomone, ako ćemo
ovo raditi, idemo onda do kraja."

00:01:30.235 --> 00:01:37.137
(Pljesak)

00:01:38.286 --> 00:01:42.191
Mogu se s time nositi.
Koliko zlata imaš?


00:01:42.215 --> 00:01:45.302
(Smijeh)

00:01:45.761 --> 00:01:48.361
On uzvrati, "Nije stvar koliko zlata imam,

00:01:48.385 --> 00:01:50.436
već je bitna tvoja sposobnost upravljanja.

00:01:50.460 --> 00:01:52.683
Možemo početi s probnom
pošiljkom od 50 kg."

00:01:52.707 --> 00:01:54.578
Uzvratih, "50 kg?

00:01:54.602 --> 00:01:56.245
Nema nikakvog smisla ovo raditi

00:01:56.269 --> 00:01:58.499
osim ako ne šaljete barem tonu."

00:01:58.523 --> 00:01:59.718
(Smijeh)

00:01:59.742 --> 00:02:02.511
(Pljesak)